external_knowledge:
- "quite popular and lucrative over the past month" refers to products with sales data within the last 30 days;
- "total sales volume" relates to `total_quantity_sold`;
- "total earnings" corresponds to `total_revenue`;
- Sorting "from the most profitable to the least profitable" means ordering by `total_revenue` in descending order.

